title: Spinach, fennel and orange salad
ingredients: ['285g baby spinach leaves', '2 oranges, peeled and sectioned', '1/2 large fennel bulb, thinly sliced', '1 teaspoon chopped fennel fronds', '4 tablespoons flaked almonds, toasted', '1 tablespoon chopped fresh mint', '3 tablespoons olive oil', '2 tablespoons orange juice', '1/2 teaspoon ground cumin', '1/2 teaspoon onion powder', 'salt and pepper to taste']
